AcqVA Aurora Workshop: From Tables to Trees Martin Schweinberger 2022-06-16 Part 1 General Information The materials for this workshop are available here. Timeline Part 1: Introduction (10:00 - 10:10) Part 2: Working with tables in R (10:10 - 12:00) Break (12:00 - 13:00) Part 3: Tree-based models (13:00 - 14:30) This workshop consists of two parts and it is aimed at beginners and intermediate users of R. Part 2 showcases how to work with and process tabulated data (tables) using R and part 3 focuses on tree-based methods. Part 2 is decidedly practical while part 3 is more focused on discussing the advantages and disadvantages of these methods (while also showing how they can be implemented).
